sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant API as Presentation API
    participant BL as Business Logic
    participant DB as Persistence Database
    participant Email as ConfirmationEmail

    opt User Registration
        User->>API: Fill out registration form
        API->>BL: Submit user data (API call)
        BL->>DB: Create user record
        DB-->>BL: Confirm storage
        BL->>Email: Trigger welcome email
        Email-->>User: Send confirmation email
        BL-->>API: Return success response
        API-->>User: Show "Welcome" message
    end

    opt Place Creation
        User->>API: Fill out place form
        Note over User, API: Requires user to be logged in
        API->>BL: Submit place data (API call)
        BL->>DB: Create place record
        DB-->>BL: Confirm record creation
        BL-->>API: Return new listing object
        API-->>User: Show success message
    end

    opt Review Submission
        User->>API: Complete review form
        Note over User, API: Requires user to be logged in
        API->>BL: Submit review data (API call)
        BL->>DB: Create review record
        DB-->>BL: Confirm review creation
        BL-->>API: Review stored and linked to place
        API-->>User: Show success message
    end

    opt Fetching a List of Places
        User->>API: Submit search query
        API->>BL: Submit search parameters (API call)
        BL->>BL: Apply filters
        BL->>DB: Query matching places
        DB-->>BL: Return place data
        BL-->>API: Results formatted for output
        API-->>User: Show properties
    end
